CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 18, 1960, pg .5 reads: "3. Jennie Jeter, nationally known home economist, ably assisted by Rosalyn (Bunny) McPherson, added to the festive fun with her droll humor as she pleased the crowds with her demonstrations of the newest recipes."
TitMainTitle: Jennie Jeter and Rosalyn (Bunny) McPherson, performing cooking demonstration in Natural Gas Companies booth in Syria Mosque for the 1960 Courier-WAMO Home-A-Rama
